---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Me"
  description="Learn more about my journey in P2P economies and distributed systems"
  pubDate={new Date("January 28 2025")}
  heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
  <div class="about-content">
    <section class="intro">
      <h2>üëã Hi, I'm Sacha Pignot</h2>
      <p>
        I'm a software developer and researcher passionate about peer-to-peer
        economies, distributed systems, and the future of economic
        collaboration. Through this blog, I explore and share insights about
        building decentralized solutions that can reshape how we think about
        economic interactions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="focus">
      <h2>üéØ My Focus</h2>
      <p>
        My work centers on understanding and developing systems that enable more
        equitable, efficient, and sustainable economic models. I'm particularly
        interested in:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>P2P Economic Systems:</strong> Exploring how peer-to-peer networks
          can create more resilient and inclusive economic structures.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Distributed Technologies:</strong> Investigating and implementing
          solutions that leverage distributed systems for economic applications.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Economic Paradigms:</strong> Studying and contributing to the development
          of new economic models that better serve society's needs.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="work">
      <h2>üíº What I Do</h2>
      <p>I combine technical expertise with economic insights to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Develop distributed applications and systems</li>
        <li>Research and write about P2P economic models</li>
        <li>Create educational content about distributed systems</li>
        <li>Contribute to open-source projects in this space</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="connect">
      <h2>ü§ù Let's Connect</h2>
      <p>
        I'm always excited to connect with others who share my interests in P2P
        economies and distributed systems. You can find me on:
      </p>
      <ul class="social-links">
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/soushi888" target="_blank">GitHub</a> - Where
          I share my code and contributions
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://x.com/soushi888" target="_blank">X (Twitter)</a> - For
          updates and discussions
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sacha-pignot/" target="_blank"
            >LinkedIn</a
          > - For professional connections
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .about-content {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    section {
      margin: 2.5em 0;
    }

    h2 {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 1.8em;
      margin: 1em 0 0.5em;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 1em 0;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    li {
      margin: 1em 0;
      padding-left: 1.5em;
      position: relative;
    }

    li::before {
      content: "‚Üí";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .social-links a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .social-links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    strong {
      color: var(--accent);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
